{"tid":1803648,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國教會牧師被判囚9年 被指涉煽動顛覆國家政權","createTime":"2019-12-30T11:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T13:46:21.000Z","uid":165683,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"107b855a6f629bfdaf34ccceb5278aac7b392f95","tid":1803648,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T11:07:47.000Z","msg":"成都秋雨聖約教會牧師王怡被判煽動顛覆國家政權及非法經營等罪成，判處有期徒刑9年，剝奪政治權利3年，沒收5萬元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n中大崇基學院神學院院長邢福增認為，今次判刑嚴重，以往家庭教會的領袖，很少以煽動顛覆國家政權入罪，王怡的情況罕有。邢福增分析，事件是對給予其他教會一個警號，因王怡曾公開批評政府政策、關心政治犯家屬、悼念六四事件等，又與家庭教會之間有聯繫，建立類似跨地域性的團隊，對中央政府來說是威脅。他認為，政府是想造出一個「樣板」，如果其他教會領袖與王怡一樣有類似舉動，要再好好思考是否想走一樣的路。<br />\n<br />\n邢福增又說，秋雨聖約教會已被取締，之前一些被捕的會友都已經被判罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500165-20191230.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500165-20191230.htm&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYjkqoP0ISDA%2F8fQ3RVu%2FF4%3D&h=0ba7d6c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500165-20191230.htm&h=ed681387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500165-20191230.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b32e42f78f938ee13b852b15aba1b859ba48744d","tid":1803648,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T11:08:10.000Z","msg":"德國聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功)</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fcontent%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_23%2FPetition_99604.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkYjkqoP0ISDA%2F8fQ3RVu%2FF4%3D&h=4d2d6dfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/content/petitionen/_2019/_09/_23/Petition_99604.html</a></span><br 